POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "content":"Epinards, Brocolis, Olives vertes, Basilic"
}

### Create a movie without info for a property
POST {{baseUrl}}/movies
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title":"Bob l'éponge",
    "content":"Etoile d'or"
}

